{"tid":1242850,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該各位香港人斬草要除根","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:39:43.000Z","uid":46763,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adc2de6985093cc14361b968ee51ccd61ff713d9","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"我哋見到所有記招 立會會議<br />\n都係用唔同既招數射波迴避問題<br />\n我唔討論 佢哋只係責任推卸 合理化自己既問題<br />\n而且掉轉指責我哋義士既行為係暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋而家仲有贏既機會<br />\n但如果唔把握好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔贏 就一定輸 係冇打和！</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n畀佢哋推下推下<br />\n件事淡咗 呢幾年都唔會敢有大議題推<br />\n<br />\n當時間流逝 往後既<span style=\"color: red;\">新血</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會係雙/單非兒童 </span> 你覺得佢會抗爭？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">90後係被選中既細路</span></span><br />\n當香港淪落變成新疆 被人思想改造<br />\n一切已經太遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請暫緩一切打飛機討論<br />\n積極討論下一步行動</span><br />\n<br />\n利申 我認為新移民而家加入抗爭<br />\n會冰釋前嫌 大和解<br />\n歡迎大家融入"},{"pid":"3d65dca76d371cf8c789fa149af831db7bffdcd2","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"中共總係想辦法令我哋本土勢力瓦解<br />\n我覺得呢一刻算係最團結既時候<br />\n唔知過後仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57106f41d2b2b311ee5ee30de3f2e30fd2ce2ebc","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800c30acc1624fe9381467ef3a6b6e032dd87549","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"558f27acbb5af0d27f2ee1e228e2d5949e4e63a5","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4097c9d5056d2f647090741aa58d05064e601d8","tid":1242850,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite